Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家注意了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.98,0:02:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼首先  大家兩人一組
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  要和誰組啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  和大哥組隊這可不敢當
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.18,0:02:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了阿寬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.22,0:02:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  雖然咱很高興您能選我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗伊阿九斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.99,0:02:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不二子大人  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
